1 AMEND House Bill No. 3230, Page 1, Section 64.296, Line 1, by deleting all of said line and
2 inserting in lieu thereof the following:
3
4 "64.296. 1. This section shall be known and may be cited as "The Missouri Affordable
5 Housing Act".
6 2. As used in this section, the following words and terms shall mean:"; and
7
8 Further amend said bill and section, Pages 1-3, Lines 33-69, by renumbering all subsequent
9 subsections accordingly; and
10
11 Further amend said bill and section, Page 3, Line 54, by inserting after the word "residences." the
12 following:
13
14 "Nothing in this section shall be construed to limit, restrict, or preempt the authority of any local
15 government to adopt, enforce, amend, or maintain any ordinance, land-use regulation, or other
16 code or regulation establishing aesthetic or architectural design for single-family homes,
17 including site-built homes, modular homes, and qualified manufactured homes, within its
18 jurisdiction. Any such ordinance, code, or regulation adopted by a local government shall apply
19 uniformly to all single-family residential construction, including site-built homes, modular
20 homes, and qualified manufactured homes, within the same zoning district."; and
21
22 Further amend said bill by amending the title, enacting clause, and intersectional references
23 accordingly.
